notesStmt.note: This conversation takes place during the lunchtime break of a one-day meeting about the European higher education area. The participants are members of various institutions and organizations involved in higher education and quality assurance. S7 hosts the meeting and invites the participants to a buffet in the seminar room where they had their discussions before. Participants thus get themselves drinks and food and come back to the table one after the other. There are multiple parallel conversations as people talk about private as well as professional matters. The transcript switches between several of these parallel conversations.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
